{"title":"初春","authors":["聂作平"],"dates":[{"year":1995,"month":2,"day":20}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"初春"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"聂作平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是南山初融的积雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是盆地起伏的蛙声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是街头解下冬装的少女"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一队队唱着进行曲的红领巾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"初春，麦苗苍翠，万物复苏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳软软的流苏披在二月的山峰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是村口一群整理犁铧的农人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是漫漫翩飞的蝴蝶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为我春天的祖国披上五彩的纱巾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"初春，城市吉祥，原野美丽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而我，一个年轻的诗人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把歌声和祈祷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"撒向都市。城镇。工厂和乡村"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}